<span class="quote1">|  1 | SIMPLE      | t1    | system | NULL          | NULL | NULL    | NULL  |</span>
  1 |             |
<span class="quote1">|  1 | SIMPLE      | t2    | ref    | ix            | ix   | 67      | const |</span>
 10 | Using where |
+----+-------------+-------+--------+---------------+------+---------+-------+--
----+-------------+
2 rows in set (0.03 sec)
